THEY REFUSED TO MAKE MY MEAL  I reserved and prepaid for 2 chicken burritos through MealPal for dinner and when I arrived at the restaurant I scanned the MP code. I showed the confirmation to the server/cook but he didn’t believe that I truly had a reservation, and then he refused to fulfill the meal request!!! Unbelievable!  This is an extremely poor display of customer service and it is needless to say that I will not be returning, using MealPal or otherwise.

Ordered to-go a chicken plate and barbacoa burrito from here, and both were equally delicious. The burrito was 12" and was filled with meat, a generous portion for its price. The chicken plate came with a side of salad and portions again were big. Definitely recommend both. The restaurant has a lot of seating, but I think of it more as a take out place. They do delivery through the apps. They're fast, but I only went at night when there weren't that many people. Great place, definitely coming back for more.

If you want authentic tacos that transport you to being in a local restaurant somewhere in Mexico or Central America look no further. I mean this in the best possible way - the soft shell tacos are dynamite and the 3 taco deal is the way to go so you can sample all the different amazing flavors. I typically go for the chicken mole, the camarron (shrimp), and the Korean BBQ taco (which might not be traditional but is so crazy good). Definitely put this on your food list and get here for a taco!
